Frankie Valli and The Four Seasons have announced they will play Glasgow's Clyde Auditorium on Monday, July 6. The real Jersey Boys: Frankie Valli and The Four Seasons announce Glasgow date Frankie Valli and The Four Seasons have announced they will play Glasgow's Clyde Auditorium on Monday, July 6.The group, famed for hits Walk Like A Man, Big Girls Don't Cry and Sherry, will be touring the UK throughout June and July.The group's story was turned into the hit musical Jersey Boys and the movie version directed by Clint Eastwood was recently released.Pre-sale for the show starts 9am on Thursday.For more information, visit www.gigsinscotland.com 